<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <title>Bienvenido</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        }

        .content {
            display: block;
            align-items: center;
            align-content: center;
            width: 100%;
            min-width: 400px;
            color: rgb(175, 1, 1);
        }

        .content-img {
            align-items: center;
            align-content: center;
        }

        .content h3 {
            font-size: 24px;
            min-width: 400px;
            text-align: center;
            align-items: center;
            align-self: center;
        }

        .content p {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        }

        .content-code {
            border: 2px solid gray;
            border-radius: 25px;
            gap: 20px;
            max-width: 150px;
            margin: auto;
        }

        .code-text {
            text-align: center;
            vertical-align: middle;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }


        .footerContent {
            width: 100%;
            display: block;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-top: 50px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            gap: 10px;
            background: rgb(175, 1, 1);
        }

        .footerContent p {
            display: block;
            font-size: 14px;
            width: 100%;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 16px;
        }

        .footerText {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding-left: 5px;
            padding-right: 5px;
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="content">
    <div class="content content-img">
        <div class="content-img">
            <img src="https://www.sendmundo.com/img/header/comremit-logo.svg" alt="SendMundo"/>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <h3>Cambio de contraseña</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <h3>Change password</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p class="subTitleText">
            Hemos recibido una solicitud de cambio de contraseña. El código de validación de su cuenta es:
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p class="subTitleText">
            We have received a request to change your password. The validation code for your account is:
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <!-- Here is the code that is sent in the email -->
        <div class="content-code">
            <p class="code-text">{{ code }}</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>
            Si no ha sido usted el que ha realizado la solicitud de cambio, no es necesario que realice ninguna acción.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p class="subTitleText">
            If you did not make the change request, you do not need to take any action.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="content footerContent">
        <p class="footerText">SendMundo Communications and Finance Technologies SL</p>
        <p class="footerText">
            Pasaje del Carme, 24, Sant Cugat del Vallés, 08173. Barcelona, España
        </p>
        <p class="footerText">CIF: B42981191</p>
        <p class="footerText">
            <a href="https://dashboard.sendmundo.com/reset-password">
                dashboard.sendmundo.com
            </a>
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
